    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安将在土耳其市政选举中惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/turkey-municipal-elections-erdogan-set-for-shock-defeat-against-main-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安(Recep Tayyip Erdogan)在投票箱中面临主要反对党的惨败，原因是通货膨胀猖獗，借贷成本达到二十多年前总统上台以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/turkey-municipal-elections-erdogan-set-for-shock-defeat-against-main-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 20:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡誓言将平民从拉法转移出来，然后粉碎哈马斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/netanyahu-vows-to-move-civilians-from-rafah-then-smash-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡表示，军方正准备将超过一百万巴勒斯坦平民撤离加沙南部城市拉法，为他们提供足够的援助，然后对那里剩余的哈马斯战斗营进行攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/netanyahu-vows-to-move-civilians-from-rafah-then-smash-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 18:27:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯、以色列和部族争夺控制权，加沙人挨饿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/gazans-go-hungry-as-hamas-israel-and-clans-battle-for-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯的一名高级警察指挥官于三月中旬会见了加沙部落的首领，他们一直在征用为饥饿的巴勒斯坦人提供的援助。他告诉他们停止接收货物，否则就会被杀。一周后，那位指挥官被杀——由以色列军队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/gazans-go-hungry-as-hamas-israel-and-clans-battle-for-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 17:11:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列央行行长警告国防支出增加的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/israel-central-banker-warns-on-impact-of-rising-defense-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列央行行长表示，以色列不断升级的国防开支对经济构成风险，需要谨慎考虑增加国防开支。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/israel-central-banker-warns-on-impact-of-rising-defense-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 14:21:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着停火压力的上升，内塔尼亚胡将进行疝气手术</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/israeli-prime-minister-netanyahu-to-undergo-hernia-operation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管以色列政府面临与哈马斯达成人质协议和停火协议的压力越来越大，但总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡将于周日晚上因疝气手术入院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/israeli-prime-minister-netanyahu-to-undergo-hernia-operation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 13:54:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国石油供应商大举进军全球欧佩克+市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/american-oil-is-muscling-into-opec-markets-all-over-the-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对俄罗斯和委内瑞拉石油制裁的主要受益者之一？美国供应商强行进入曾经由欧佩克及其盟友主导的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/american-oil-is-muscling-into-opec-markets-all-over-the-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>查尔斯国王诊断癌症后出席复活节仪式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/king-charles-will-attend-easter-service-providing-a-glimpse-of-the-monarch-after-cancer-diagnosis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦（美联社）——周日，国王查理三世在温莎城堡参加复活节仪式后与旁观者握手并聊天，这是他自上个月被诊断患有癌症以来最重要的公开活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/king-charles-will-attend-easter-service-providing-a-glimpse-of-the-monarch-after-cancer-diagnosis</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 09:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对党领袖被捕后，数千人在德里举行集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/thousands-attend-a-rally-in-india-s-capital-to-challenge-prime-minister-modi-ahead-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新德里（美联社）——印度反对党联盟周日举行大规模集会，发起竞选活动，批评总理纳伦德拉·莫迪政府在下个月的全国大选前压制对手并破坏民主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/thousands-attend-a-rally-in-india-s-capital-to-challenge-prime-minister-modi-ahead-of-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 09:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教宗在圣彼得广场主持复活节周日弥撒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/pope-overcomes-health-concerns-presides-over-blustery-easter-sunday-mass-in-st-peter-s-square</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马（美联社）——周日，教皇方济各在经历了长达冬季的呼吸道疾病困扰后重整旗鼓，带领约 6 万人参加复活节庆祝活动，强烈呼吁加沙停火以及俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的囚犯交换。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/pope-overcomes-health-concerns-presides-over-blustery-easter-sunday-mass-in-st-peter-s-square</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 08:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安的政党在市政投票的早期结果中落后于对手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/erdogan-faces-tight-race-in-turkish-cities-in-local-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据国家广播公司 TRT 公布的初步结果，土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安的执政党将在市政选举中遭遇主要反对派的重大挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/erdogan-faces-tight-race-in-turkish-cities-in-local-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
